MasterCommander — Future Plans & Design Notes

Boat Change Detection (Plan)  
Date: 2026-02-25, Priority: Plan before building  

Problem: Detect boat changes on cloud connection (fleet reassignment, surveyor/device on multiple boats, delivery puck usage).  
Constraints: Offline Commander app; detection on Master Cloud; surveyors may be offline.  
Key question: Detect usage on multiple boats without cloud.  
Ideas:  
- Hardware fingerprinting via NMEA2000 signatures, store locally and flag changes.  
- SignalK vessel identity changes (MMSI, name).  
- Cloud sync next connection with fingerprint history to detect mismatches.  
- Require new boat assessment on cloud connection.  
- Offline enforcement: require confirmation on mismatch at startup.  
- License tied to boat fingerprint; transfer requires explicit action.
